---
// Problem Section Component
---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-stone-50" data-scroll-fade>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 border border-orange-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
        </svg>
        The Problem
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-black leading-tight mb-4">
        What's Missing in Today's School System?
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Swipe through the key issues in modern education
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Horizontal Scroll Container -->
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Navigation Buttons -->
      <button id="problemPrevBtn" class="absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-10 bg-white/90 hover:bg-white text-black p-3 rounded-full shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
      </button>
      
      <button id="problemNextBtn" class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-10 bg-white/90 hover:bg-white text-black p-3 rounded-full shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </button>

      <!-- Scroll Container -->
      <div id="problemScrollContainer" class="overflow-x-auto scrollbar-hide mx-8" style="scroll-snap-type: x mandatory; scroll-behavior: smooth;">
        <div class="flex gap-8 pb-4">
          <!-- Panel 1: Hands-on Exposure -->
          <div class="flex-none w-80 lg:w-96 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 scroll-snap-align-start border border-gray-200 shadow-lg">
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Missing Hands-On Exposure</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                In today's school system, what's missing is <strong class="text-black">hands-on exposure</strong> — 
                the kind that connects classroom learning to how things actually work in the real world.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
                <p class="text-orange-700 text-sm font-medium">
                  Students learn theory but miss practical application
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Panel 2: Behind the Scenes -->
          <div class="flex-none w-80 lg:w-96 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 scroll-snap-align-start border border-gray-200 shadow-lg">
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">No Behind-the-Scenes Understanding</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Students are already exploring multiple interests — coding, creating, designing, experimenting — 
                yet they rarely understand what really goes on <strong class="text-black">behind the scenes</strong>. 
                Why wait until college to figure that out?
              </p>
              <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
                <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
                  Curiosity exists but lacks real-world context
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Panel 3: Flow of Understanding -->
          <div class="flex-none w-80 lg:w-96 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 scroll-snap-align-start border border-gray-200 shadow-lg">
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Broken Flow of Understanding</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Even engineering graduates often spend years trying to understand what they truly want to do. 
                Not because they lack capability, but because there's no <strong class="text-black">flow of understanding</strong> 
                that links their learning to real-world application.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
                <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
                  Graduates struggle with career direction
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Panel 4: Endless Learning Loop -->
          <div class="flex-none w-80 lg:w-96 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 scroll-snap-align-start border border-gray-200 shadow-lg">
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">The Endless Learning Loop</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Many end up stuck in a loop of endless learning, without clarity or direction. 
                They consume content but never gain the confidence to apply their knowledge meaningfully.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
                <p class="text-orange-700 text-sm font-medium">
                  Learning without purpose leads to confusion
                </p>
              </div>
              <!-- Animated dots -->
              <div class="flex justify-center space-x-2 mt-6">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full animate-bounce"></div>
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full animate-bounce" style="animation-delay: 0.1s"></div>
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full animate-bounce" style="animation-delay: 0.2s"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scroll Indicators -->
      <div class="flex justify-center mt-8 space-x-2">
        <div id="problemIndicator0" class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full transition-all duration-300"></div>
        <div id="problemIndicator1" class="w-2 h-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full transition-all duration-300"></div>
        <div id="problemIndicator2" class="w-2 h-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full transition-all duration-300"></div>
        <div id="problemIndicator3" class="w-2 h-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full transition-all duration-300"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- The Missing Layer Section -->
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
        Understanding the Learning Gap
      </h3>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Enhance your educational experience with our comprehensive approach, 
        offering deeper insights and meaningful connections for modern learning needs.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Card Layout Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 h-auto lg:h-96">
      <!-- Large Feature Card (Left) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400/15 to-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white relative overflow-hidden h-full">
        <!-- Gradient Background -->
       
        
        <!-- Background Pattern -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
          <svg class="w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 400 300" fill="none">
            <circle cx="350" cy="50" r="80" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="250" r="60" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"/>
            <path d="M200 100L250 150L200 200L150 150Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
              Bridging the Gap
            </span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
              Our knowledge inspires us to innovate continuously
            </h4>
            <p class="text-emerald-100 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              We connect the "what" and "how" of learning with the crucial "why" - 
              transforming curiosity into clarity and learning into understanding.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <button class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 rounded-lg text-white font-medium transition-colors duration-200 self-start">
            Explore Our Approach
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Column - 2x2 Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-rows-2 gap-6 h-full">
        <!-- Top Right Card - Sky Blue -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400/20 to-cyan-500/15 rounded-2xl p-6 text-white relative h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-sky-100 mb-2">Deep Understanding Through</p>
                <h5 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Why-Based Learning</h5>
              </div>
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 opacity-60 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sky-100 text-sm">
              Connecting knowledge to real-world purpose and meaning.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Bottom Right Card - Dark Gray -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-700 to-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6 text-white relative h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
            <h5 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Complete Learning Solutions</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Comprehensive educational strategies that bridge theory with practical application, 
              ensuring students understand not just what and how, but why.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-end mt-4">
          
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
      
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Bottom Section -->
    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Left Card - Sky Blue -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500/15 to-cyan-600/20 rounded-2xl border border-sky-500/30 p-8 relative">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sky-300 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Innovative Solutions Driving Educational</p>
            <h5 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Knowledge Integration</h5>
          </div>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sky-200">
          Transforming traditional learning approaches by connecting classroom knowledge 
          to real-world applications and industry insights.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Card - Summary -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/15 to-gray-600/20 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-700 relative">
        <h5 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 via-orange-300 to-gray-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          That "Why" Connects Knowledge to Purpose
        </h5>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          It transforms curiosity into clarity, and learning into understanding. 
          That's the gap we're bridging - creating meaningful connections between 
          what students learn and why it matters in the real world.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>